<text top="1082" left="90" width="6" height="14" font="9"><b>2</b></text>
<text top="88" left="90" width="62" height="14" font="9"><b>A/57/PV.84</b></text>
<text top="132" left="126" width="115" height="17" font="5"><i>It was so decided.</i></text>
<text top="159" left="126" width="324" height="17" font="7"><b>The Acting President</b>: May I therefore take it</text>
<text top="177" left="90" width="360" height="17" font="2">that the Assembly wishes to declare Canada elected a</text>
<text top="195" left="90" width="360" height="17" font="2">member of the Committee for Programme and</text>
<text top="213" left="90" width="360" height="17" font="2">Coordination for a term of office beginning on 1 May</text>
<text top="231" left="90" width="270" height="17" font="2">2003 and expiring on 31 December 2005?</text>
<text top="258" left="126" width="115" height="17" font="5"><i>It was so decided.</i></text>
<text top="132" left="504" width="324" height="17" font="7"><b>The Acting President</b>: I congratulate Canada on</text>
<text top="150" left="468" width="360" height="17" font="2">its election as a member of the Committee for</text>
<text top="168" left="468" width="194" height="17" font="2">Programme and Coordination.</text>
<text top="195" left="504" width="324" height="17" font="2">We have thus concluded our consideration of</text>
<text top="213" left="468" width="102" height="17" font="2">agenda item 16.</text>
<text top="240" left="504" width="196" height="17" font="5"><i>The meeting rose at 10.15 a.m.</i></text>
</page>
